<p>Asset security and attractive added value are compatible with each other; Diamonds are among the most valuable materials and have always been used not only as jewelry, but also for the storage and transportation of assets.</p>
<h1>Our Philosophy</h1>
<p>LOEWENGART is an association of experts from the diamond industry and the financial industry. It brings together two worlds that coexisted for many years without really interacting.</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">The mission of LOEWENGART is to provide a secure and transparent investment that works on a permanent basis. Our offer is aimed at private and institutional clients worldwide, who have a special need for security and discretion. </span></p>
